version_description: This publishing it for the more beginner player that may not be familiar with some of the chords in the other tabs. This is not the way the original song was written, but it's a more simple alternative. There are only two difficult chords which are the Gb and the Gbm and they are only played one time, so if you're just starting out, you can actually just omit them. You can play a 4 finger F chord, and it's not barred either.
Maroon 5 performed a Al Green's Hit Song.
